description: A river of Samnium and a major tributary of the Volturno river.
details:
The Barrington Atlas Directory notes: Calore

Â 
On the banks of the Calor, three miles from Beneventum, T. Sempronius Gracchus defeated Hanno the Elder in 214 BC.
